<br>
She seemed ok but definatly in with the wrong crowd as he could sense her fright. It angered him that vampires would use their powers against eachother in such a way for he only used his if provoked. By what he could tell she had done nothing so far. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Its time you changed company my dear Iris...</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> he thought to himself as the effects of the smoke and garlic gas wore off and the vampire ordered the others found.<br>
